00:14:33.259 --> 00:14:35.259
Here we read,

00:14:35.259 --> 00:14:38.259
Do not be misled.

00:14:38.259 --> 00:14:40.259
God is not one to be mocked.

00:14:40.259 --> 00:14:45.259
For whatever a person is sowing, this he will also reap.

00:14:45.259 --> 00:14:51.259
